description: The memo that Natalia V. Veselnitskaya, a Russian lawyer, brought with her to a meeting at Trump Tower in June 2016 closely followed a document that the Russian prosecutor general's office had given to an American congressman two months earlier, incorporating some paragraphs verbatim.
title: Read the Talking Points Shared With the Kremlin
title_page: Read the Talking Points Shared With the Kremlin - The New York Times
